=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都成日影底 <br />\n睇醫生食藥過幾日就好"},{"pid":"1a493a8f9fa222cfcd99b6a4d9c586fc326c1f60","tid":732100,"uid":17606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:10:58.000Z","msg":"飛滋？<br />\n如果係就肯定手足口病 生過"},{"pid":"e355ff979f374b9ee6a3958ef6c4fb193598e513","tid":732100,"uid":130586,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ef68402b1afc133a56f384a9d7cc00250a330e8a","tid":732100,"uid":76087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:46:32.000Z","msg":"以前試過手足口病都係生到咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:19:15.000Z","msg":"Touchwood真係手足口病會傅染<br />\n樓主快啲睇醫生<br />\n勤洗手 唔好周圍掂<br />\n儘量避免同人接觸 尤其是小朋友"},{"pid":"63de278ba33cc7e1db3389c4916f4752b2eb15eb","tid":732100,"uid":81190,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:19:16.000Z","msg":"連登醫院已額滿<br />\n急診室醫生通通蛇王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依圖可見應非大問題<br />\n煩請到就近之診所及急診室求診，不日內便將康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後祝君安康，早日痊癒"},{"pid":"0daf6ee855622cd40d9bc4f4831ccc51cf0fae12","tid":732100,"uid":40933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:19:22.000Z","msg":"普通發炎"},{"pid":"3568dd35eb36f87eec038f05720a70952edc793e","tid":732100,"uid":84367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"7125f96cf7230ab0c72eacec0156f2c4dab2921d","tid":732100,"uid":19068,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:30:15.000Z","msg":"少嘢啦，我以前試過嚴重發炎，你幅圖點個啲位差唔多全部都係飛滋，白色一粒粒，最大個粒有手指公指甲咁大，仲要痴埋一齊生，睇完醫生食消炎，抗生，喉糖就好快冇事，盡快求醫啦"},{"pid":"8926924ca296cf3c88876e9861b904da584fa2e6","tid":732100,"uid":121091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"試過仲嚴重過你 生曬呢啲 仲有啲白色既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為自己個喉嚨會爛 嚇死<br />\n之後睇醫生開抗生素 好快就無事"},{"pid":"703ed2f741b305db5dd4359dd7c268975bf27dea","tid":732100,"uid":114158,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:51:54.000Z","msg":"認真答，扁桃腺發炎 會痛不欲生好似俾十萬支針拮緊喉嚨咁。我年中痛過唔少次，每次都同發燒打孖上，睇醫生或者飲多兩杯涼茶就會消 好快無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f101d314d248d81f6a2645944d3b56bd6494aab","tid":732100,"uid":109086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:06:07.000Z","msg":"我喉嚨長期都類似樓主咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但唔會痛"},{"pid":"eccc5055f650e273931060d99edf76ac8a7792bf","tid":732100,"uid":149852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:09:48.000Z","msg":"似手足口 睇吓醫生好喎"},{"pid":"46a28ab7eb35c4ae555abeab5e8dc3bf30b73889","tid":732100,"uid":154793,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:15:23.000Z","msg":"我兩年都生咗幾粒，完全冇理過，仲喺度<br />\n你check到咩黎話我知 thx"},{"pid":"408d96bfb90e600e5430fcaad291d0fe83226c34","tid":732100,"uid":167186,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:28:21.000Z","msg":"影得咁清 樓主都幾勁"},{"pid":"a16233e4206cb331feb955296f1c249cba91588b","tid":732100,"uid":4677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:47:07.000Z","msg":"喉嚨生白點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都試過，嗰時仲要去澳門，痛到食buffet都無胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 吞口水都痛到仆街<br />\n<br />\n生左成個幾禮拜先無，好痛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw如果你隻手 生左一點點就有機會係手足口病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9945ef0fe83d9a1c3dc34da695c239cbe8a28ffd","tid":732100,"uid":136535,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:52:02.000Z","msg":"似手足口喎"},{"pid":"f9b6b2b44e784807dcd0727bd67d917ee507b239","tid":732100,"uid":134666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T19:57:54.000Z","msg":"白色珍珠呢？"},{"pid":"87553e7f6d5017b4252eb72494cfe41dcff2ffbf","tid":732100,"uid":16096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:01:00.000Z","msg":"我照鏡 <br />\n個1同你一樣 不過唔痛的"},{"pid":"ce8aa6cc28c1b060d658253640fcb9f7c71046b3","tid":732100,"uid":98777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:02:38.000Z","msg":"睇專科食抗生素"},{"pid":"1954523d6b3c69c5550fd6898b262eae3b0857de","tid":732100,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:13:36.000Z","msg":"性病"},{"pid":"c1903fcf57bd79bc8aa0c122d947b13303d00841","tid":732100,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:15:34.000Z","msg":"花柳"},{"pid":"ffaa34eb3f566295273cfe4f9b02c627dc15dee9","tid":732100,"uid":154221,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"fbbef9e9d3421b1bcc3b48ca085880ef78736291","tid":732100,"uid":185527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:28:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾日喉嚨又試發炎 平時我起碼每個月都個喉嚨痛一次 痛既程度就好似發炎咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n頭先照鏡見到個啲一粒粒野 有冇人知係咩黎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n飛滋？？<br />\n2同3位置係發炎先會腫 <br />\n有冇人會喉嚨腫到好似我咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(有圖小心)<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png&h=30640fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我究竟幾時先好返同斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好report我啦我真係好辛苦先出post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:17:00.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣 而且都係連登問過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔痛 之後我日日食生果<br />\n戒熱氣野 早晚嗽口水及刷牙 用埋必妥碘噴喉嚨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終于都係冇分别 一樣咁多咽喉濾泡 頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765d1f5270f6a51bd2f6ef695a1dddfb67e81efa","tid":732100,"uid":75297,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:21:03.000Z","msg":"我係過來人<br />\n樓主扁桃腺發炎係一定要睇醫生食佢開嘅抗生素先斷 食足成個療程 一般10-14天左右 先好得曬<br />\n呢D如果唔好好護理 第時好易翻發<br />\n我細個就係唔知呢D野 屋企人冇為意 搞到依家長期扁桃腺都好大粒 又紅又腫 好易食少少炸野就熱氣會痛<br />\n所以趁早好醫好佢 呢段期間多D休息 補充足夠的水分 用鹽水漱口 避免食刺激野<br />\n希望你快D好翻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2349383f4e5efdd84e0bd15dbf0afa789e7d99","tid":732100,"uid":134012,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:22:44.000Z","msg":"正常熱氣 飲多兩啖水就好"},{"pid":"b82581e67355823d7c46985c58733f21ceb8e4bc","tid":732100,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:22:54.000Z","msg":"似係沙士"},{"pid":"c2bd11ad1419016427ac2aa6eb1d706e557784a2","tid":732100,"uid":36389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:24:29.000Z","msg":"噴betadine"},{"pid":"831a51c3fd913a73882839689921c030a1866c2b","tid":732100,"uid":99720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:58:00.000Z","msg":"淋巴濾泡腫脹，醫好喉嚨感染就冇事"},{"pid":"57ac2549f5426c722df1267ba51c992998e94523","tid":732100,"uid":32627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T21:10:13.000Z","msg":"即刻去醫院啦仲開po<br />\n早排女友就好似你咁入咗院訓咗兩晚係咁打抗生素<br />\n啲粒粒嚴重起上嚟去到你氣管影響你呼吸就大件事"},{"pid":"8f37d5ad0315391ed92e7d3b5d2d15413290d054","tid":732100,"uid":107990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T21:33:59.000Z","msg":"我長期都係咁<br />\n是咪玩完？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabcfdfb9638fe2582778249566190638ede7573","tid":732100,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:07:14.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺發炎啊<br />\n早啲休息唔得再睇醫生啦<br />\n以前我都問過醫生 佢話啲水泡身體差作感冒就會有<br />\n早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85ec5d2054cea8947a9522680c62ef80cf01d930","tid":732100,"uid":22700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:23:46.000Z","msg":"手腳有冇痕先 <br />\n無既話又唔係手足口"},{"pid":"6c181f6d88e05df356de6a19aa9c2bd2def59e73","tid":732100,"uid":19082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T23:55:52.000Z","msg":"個口同樓主一樣<br />\n好耐之前問過醫生佢話冇事<br />\n我話腫左喎<br />\n佢答我你又知正常人個口入面唔係咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb09c4d97d1f9c10756cc48862a9b1e80dcc775d","tid":732100,"uid":10351,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:13:47.000Z","msg":"我喉嚨長期都係咁<br />\n我以為係正常"},{"pid":"466f0f1088bad6f01ffb816681e5a0e38ca076bd","tid":732100,"uid":157669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:15:44.000Z","msg":"嘩屌你高清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b507367c1589e5349ff870c4c9de9cb57063fb93","tid":732100,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:17:53.000Z","msg":"含完撚？"},{"pid":"a2d9ec616578578cefc4c2bc41456755086ee835","tid":732100,"uid":158601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:23:32.000Z","msg":"我喉嚨都長期係咁，係咪叫慢性咽喉炎？"},{"pid":"1761814a521991d0ea334d7bf439d5ab0a5e0406","tid":732100,"uid":177313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"140bb1762708fdcc7e5ce0aa20bae24bd3794a0d","tid":732100,"uid":185527,"like":1,"dislike":74,"score":-73,"quote":{"pid":"c57523c98d1317a0aaeedbd402c41038b8d9a6c7","tid":732100,"uid":41458,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:34:12.000Z","msg":"睇左醫生未?<br />\n試下轉醫生?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T17:42:08.000Z","msg":"冇睇啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為除左喉嚨痛之外又冇咩其他症狀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"988f51d104ab59b59509fedd7526be7675a398e7","tid":732100,"uid":152598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:32:23.000Z","msg":"睇醫生啦 仲問"},{"pid":"d82a42592e5108d6817963823a11ec5b2ccdfbef","tid":732100,"uid":26332,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:42:25.000Z","msg":"究竟一個人有幾垃圾幾on9，有醫生唔睇，走上連登問？真係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得你生癌呀，快撚啲死左去啦"},{"pid":"2ed7626f97a493c16f98ed9699df672791e5bae8","tid":732100,"uid":133808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:45:04.000Z","msg":"之前試過咁 醫生話喉嚨細菌感染<br />\n食左10幾日抗生素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n醫生都睇左2次先好"},{"pid":"60d52e2e2e5f88814a62d6e2aadc4c59aaecae3b","tid":732100,"uid":22117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"其實點樣揸機可以影到咁入又咁高清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3530b84342d75163f26b1c28c20160ec8452e9fb","tid":732100,"uid":61271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:00:23.000Z","msg":"只係普通喉嚨發炎<br />\n<br />\n其實大家知唔知扁桃腺喺邊？<br />\n<br />\n手足口病亦都唔係咁樣"},{"pid":"04fe7e187cc8036738ad28603d0d82a97c6bee14","tid":732100,"uid":193004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:01:01.000Z","msg":"有病唔睇醫生上網問？<br />\n問完知咩病會好返？"},{"pid":"3f28553a06e9be755670e3aa158d39ca0e65a67e","tid":732100,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1caef40758c7d35eb233e090fbedf33a7ae9064","tid":732100,"uid":69395,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T18:03:32.000Z","msg":"幅圖2、3位置都幾肯定係扁桃腺嚟，你話會腫脤睇怕有發炎，都係睇睇醫生好啲<br />\n另外吞口水痛都可以有好多原因，不一定只係喉嚨/扁桃腺發炎<br />\n想問下樓豬除左以上癥狀外，有冇發現其他問題，如流膿，喉嚨有白點，呼吸困難等等? 因為你記得越多對醫生診斷越有幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申: 學藝未精嘅垃圾，唔敢老點樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:03:59.000Z","msg":"你去睇下tonsillitis 既clinical photos 先"},{"pid":"9e07ef7e59b7b395f351a5d4226624a226bd5090","tid":732100,"uid":55523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:04:44.000Z","msg":"飲鹽水"},{"pid":"471efbf0411807e29f5b6dd0e9db9333ca62d5a4","tid":732100,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:04:50.000Z","msg":"睇醫生喇,"},{"pid":"840dd815cb967700f01be01eaad31f662e6a5afc","tid":732100,"uid":127453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:17:37.000Z","msg":"好似係性病黎、問下ck妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e11b02d2b3d4efae775b0c647e3ab5ecb4c502d","tid":732100,"uid":107166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:24:20.000Z","msg":"扁桃腺發炎 可以用betadine漱口緩和下先"},{"pid":"d474639154769bbeda306d737d8c2e1d3395da79","tid":732100,"uid":54616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"影得好好"},{"pid":"7ff2d92c71837c8a1b45116e6af53ff5a77b58f8","tid":732100,"uid":72173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":