kgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(有圖小心)<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png&h=30640fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我究竟幾時先好返同斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好report我啦我真係好辛苦先出post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T03:55:28.000Z","msg":"消炎藥，清熱酷"},{"pid":"28eef9bfaf3a26b4ab64f865f5a0e0eb00077f27","tid":732100,"uid":162022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:08:11.000Z","msg":"仲唔去睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8c733d8ee7820a6de67ff6a67c0c51a324527b","tid":732100,"uid":185527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d52e2e2e5f88814a62d6e2aadc4c59aaecae3b","tid":732100,"uid":22117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T01:55:11.000Z","msg":"其實點樣揸機可以影到咁入又咁高清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:09:04.000Z","msg":"用電話前鏡 對住塊鏡較好個位 然後開閃燈影<br />\n佢會自動對焦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2df1b5092ed7d15040b5f6e79235edfd9408c5","tid":732100,"uid":185527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85ec5d2054cea8947a9522680c62ef80cf01d930","tid":732100,"uid"