ji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n(有圖小心)<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/07/012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F07%2F012116_92190f849cf985ae81ef6b7358a95aa5.png&h=30640fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我究竟幾時先好返同斷尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好report我啦我真係好辛苦先出post問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T20:17:00.000Z","msg":"我同你一樣 而且都係連登問過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我唔痛 之後我日日食生果<br />\n戒熱氣野 早晚嗽口水及刷牙 用埋必妥碘噴喉嚨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n終于都係冇分别 一樣咁多咽喉濾泡 頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:13:24.000Z","msg":"笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"cebb61d86af8b1126c19f77ca8183d7295232ab1","tid":732100,"uid":22585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"睇醫生，呢幾日一定每日用漱口水"},{"pid":"3bd0419661da4da354f24d17aa4ecf4f2a2c9b1c","tid":732100,"uid":30090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T04:17:36.000Z","msg":"我成日諗 身體有問題會選擇上連登問既人 係低能吖 覺得連登仔好叻吖 覺得自己死左都無所謂吖定點？"},{"pid":"2b31249abcf4c810d13741954dcf0f3c13e081ae","tid":732100,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":